==English==

===Alternative forms===
*[[cartesian coordinates]] (''US'')

===Noun===
'''[[Cartesian]] [[coordinates]]''' ''pl''

# {{alggeom}} The [[coordinate]]s of a point measured as its [[perpendicular distance]] to the right of a vertical axis (the [[y-axis|''y''-axis]]) and its perpendicular distance above a horizontal axis (the [[x-axis|''x''-axis]]).

